WEBVTT

00:00.112 --> 00:01.593
Previously on The O.C.

00:01.664 --> 00:03.368
Is it just me, or is Zach perfect?

00:03.468 --> 00:05.374
He is like Newport's Prince William.

00:05.474 --> 00:09.210
I get nervous, and I start talking,
and then nothing can shut me up.

00:09.385 --> 00:10.175
Except that.

00:10.176 --> 00:13.926
I have missed you all day.
Does this count as adultery?

00:14.011 --> 00:15.859
You're not, like,
becoming friends, are you?

00:15.873 --> 00:16.715
Would that be so terrible?

00:16.815 --> 00:17.976
Really? You don't go to school?

00:18.076 --> 00:22.381
I got kicked out. Of Corona, Mater Dei
and even Newport Union.

00:22.461 --> 00:27.722
16 years ago I made an error in judgment,
one that almost ruined my marriage.

00:28.025 --> 00:29.792
You're my father?

00:36.780 --> 00:39.697
- Hey, man, what's going on?
- Studying.

00:39.797 --> 00:42.748
Would you punch someone, please,
for old time's sake?

00:43.637 --> 00:47.147
All right, fine, logarithms are
the new uppercut, I got it.

00:49.611 --> 00:52.551
- Wow. Now I see it.
- See what?

00:52.772 --> 00:54.427
I been looking through
old photos of my mom,

00:54.464 --> 00:57.414
looking for resemblances to Lindsay.
Look at that.

00:57.429 --> 00:59.602
Are you trying to make this
more awkward for me?

00:59.803 --> 01:02.320
What? It's not like you dating
Lindsay's full-on incest

01:02.321 --> 01:04.524
you're not even really related.
You're not--

01:04.623 --> 01:07.650
you wouldn't get arrested, you wouldn't
have chromosomally challenged children.

01:07.750 --> 01:12.031
Kirsten's, like, my mom.
Lindsay is... clearly her sister.

01:12.131 --> 01:13.209
It is kind of weird.

01:13.309 --> 01:16.534
The fact that your mom doesn't know that
I'm dating her sister, it's a lot weird.

01:16.634 --> 01:19.197
I think they did a storyline
like this on The Valley once.

01:19.404 --> 01:20.917
Great, could you tell me
how it ends, then?

01:21.017 --> 01:23.204
Well, you just have to ask
yourself the question, Ryan:

01:23.348 --> 01:25.872
is she your girlfriend,
or is she your aunt?

01:25.884 --> 01:28.313
Ah, yes, the age-old question.

01:28.413 --> 01:30.827
That's right.
it's a story as old as time, really.

01:31.068 --> 01:32.767
Boy meets girl, boy likes girl,

01:32.867 --> 01:36.611
boy finds out girl is surrogate mother's
illegitimate half-sister.

01:36.751 --> 01:40.043
I'm guessing it's too soon
to joke, Seth, even for a Cohen.

01:40.224 --> 01:42.868
I just don't know what to do,
you know? What to say.

01:42.968 --> 01:44.189
Well, have you talked to Lindsay?

01:44.289 --> 01:47.871
Nah, wanted to give her space over winter
break, let her figure everything out.

01:47.971 --> 01:49.353
That's all you can do.

01:49.469 --> 01:52.318
And if she comes back and decides
she wants to be part of this family...

01:52.418 --> 01:53.689
Then we're done dating, huh?

01:53.789 --> 01:56.027
Unless you want to move to the South.

01:56.368 --> 01:57.943
Kirsten doesn't know
you're seeing Lindsay, right?

01:58.043 --> 01:58.901
She thinks we're just friends.

01:59.001 --> 02:02.420
Good, 'cause I think it's best
that the Mrs. doesn't find out.

02:02.508 --> 02:05.556
Well, that's something that
every wife wants to hear.

02:06.076 --> 02:10.138
- Doesn't find out what?
- How much I love you?

02:10.264 --> 02:11.553
- Sandy?
- Yes?

02:11.653 --> 02:13.553
You don't have to lie to me.

02:13.661 --> 02:17.163
I know that Renee's testimony is today,
and that my father is going free.

02:17.165 --> 02:19.071
- Yeah.
- Sharp as a tack.

02:19.071 --> 02:20.713
Just, it's, like, a laser beam.

02:20.813 --> 02:22.806
But that doesn't mean
I have to forgive him.

02:22.867 --> 02:25.876
Not after what he did
to Lindsay, that poor girl.

02:27.198 --> 02:30.838
I've been thinking.
We should do something for her.

02:31.114 --> 02:36.172
This girl grew up not knowing who she is
or where she's from, and we're her family.

02:36.207 --> 02:38.223
- If she wants us.
- Oh, she wants us.

02:38.256 --> 02:39.415
I mean... you guys.

02:39.515 --> 02:43.244
Well, you, too, Ryan-- you're as much
a part of this family as any of us.

02:43.417 --> 02:45.847
I mean, if she's my sister,
she's your aunt.

02:45.930 --> 02:47.603
Well, thanks for clearing
that one up, honey.

02:47.703 --> 02:50.560
Actually, she's so young,
she's more like your sister.

02:50.783 --> 02:54.437
Oh. Hey, a sister.
I always wanted one of those.

02:54.795 --> 02:56.927
Ryan, how about you?

02:57.421 --> 03:03.231
The O.C. 207, OC team
Cookie, Synchro VO Scidou

